'''Dactyl''' was a yellow-[[Color/Legends|colored]] [[Ammonia/Legends|ammonia]] [[Crystal/Legends|crystal]]. It was essential to the survival of [[Arcona/Legends|Arcona]] when away from the ammonia-rich [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]] of their [[Cona/Legends|homeworld]]. Arcona who went without dactyl quickly faded from a green to grayish muddy tan, shed scales, and eventually [[Death/Legends|died]].

[[Salt/Legends|Salt]] was known to dramatically increase an Arconan's need of dactyl.

